  "title": "Part-time Sales Associate",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Serve as the primary face of the brand, managing the customer experience and effectively selling products.</li>\n  <li>Drive product sales by not only meeting personal sales targets but also contributing to the achievement of overall Boutique targets.</li>\n  <li>Uphold high standards of customer service by consistently delivering an exceptional experience to customers.</li>\n  <li>Actively promote and sell products by adeptly identifying customers' needs and providing personalized recommendations to meet those needs.</li>\n  <li>Ensure the Boutique maintains an impeccable appearance, adhering to established standards.</li>\n  <li>Take responsibility for the proper presentation of products, aligning with specifications and creating an inviting display environment.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Good communication skills</li>\n  <li>Cheerful, self-motivated with positive attitude </li>\n  <li>Outgoing team player with strong interpersonal and communication skills</li>\n  <li>Customer &amp; sales oriented</li>\n  <li>Professional presentation</li>\n  <li>Able to work on shifts </li>\n</ul>",
